  "title": "Administrative Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Efficiently handle documentation and filing tasks.</li><li>Regularly check and replenish office supplies such as stationery and pantry items.</li><li>Assist in the completion of daily administrative tasks.</li><li>Manage incoming phone calls and greet visitors professionally.</li><li>Support other tasks as assigned by the superior or Director.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in the related field.</li><li>Proficient in speaking and writing in English.</li><li>Demonstrated ability to meet deadlines and deal with competing priorities.</li><li>Excellent attention to detail, including proofreading and editing skills.</li><li>Ability to independently resolve routine problems and issues.</li></ul>",
